          "reviewBody": "My daughter was in school for 2 years.First year we had good experience,however, during the second year her class teacher has been changed it wasn't motivating change. She never took any action against theft or misbehavior. During PTM, whenever we raised concern, she was like will look into it, which has never happened. Finally we changed school and we are happy with the difference we see in school.\nThey also suggest you take an extramarks subscription, which is fraud. Do not purchase it and waste your money and time.",
